unittitle_ssm: Time Inc. Fortune Publishing and Business Records
abstract_ssm: The Fortune Publishing and Business Records contain materials from the offices and staff of the business and publishing side of the magazine's operation. The majority of materials are records from from the office of Publisher William Geer; advertiser record cards; and records from the offices of public affairs and promotions.
